Package com.livelife.motolibrary

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OnAntEventListener
    The main ANT events listener, implement it in your activity and override the onMessageReceived(byte[] message) and onAntServiceConnected() methods to get ANT events in your code.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AntData
    AntData contains all the constants and methods used to configure the MOTO tile look and behaviour.
    MotoConnection
    The MotoConnection is a singleton class that manages the MOTO tiles setup and display
    usage: MotoConnection.getInstance().startMotoConnection(activity, deviceId);
    MotoSound
    MotoSound is a class used to trigger sounds in a MOTO application.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AntConnectionException
